WEBVTT

00:05:27.101 --> 00:05:31.085
to do what no one
has been able to do until now:

00:05:31.109 --> 00:05:36.212
measure methane pollution
from oil and gas facilities worldwide,

00:05:36.236 --> 00:05:38.116
with exacting precision.

00:05:38.664 --> 00:05:42.156
Its data stream will allow us
to map that pollution,

00:05:42.180 --> 00:05:44.047
so that everyone can see it.

00:05:44.712 --> 00:05:47.093
Then it's all about
turning data into action,

00:05:47.117 --> 00:05:49.489
just as we did in the United States.

00:05:49.513 --> 00:05:54.728
We've seen that when we present
companies with data,

00:05:54.752 --> 00:05:57.152
many of them will cut the pollution.

00:05:58.379 --> 00:06:01.434
Citizens will be empowered to take action;